      "author": "hugoroasted (hugo@newvoice.gg)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi,<br />\nI am using the widget “goals” from monday, with the X line by dates of commissions. But it filter by increase: the month with the most commissions goes in 1st, etc. But I want it just to be “january, february” etc, whatever the commissions are.</p>\n<p>Do you have any idea?</p>\n<p>Many thanks !<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/a/0/a00c93f4f69f1ca045cbde2e99d151e496d7827d.png\" title=\"Capture d’écran 2024-01-08 à 19.47.58\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/a/0/a00c93f4f69f1ca045cbde2e99d151e496d7827d_2_690x171.png\" alt=\"Capture d’écran 2024-01-08 à 19.47.58\" width=\"690\" height=\"171\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Capture d’écran 2024-01-08 à 19.47.58</span><span class=\"informations\">1120×279 13.7 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
