      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/hugoroasted\">@hugoroasted</a></p>\n<p>Can you show us your board ? I tried, Monday displays my dates by month, without considering the amount of commissions.</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/a/ba9ca7aaa0ce25b2ac133d0e4d3e64cd9c014f6d.png\" title=\"Capture d’écran 2024-01-08 à 20.29.03\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/a/ba9ca7aaa0ce25b2ac133d0e4d3e64cd9c014f6d_2_690x423.png\" alt=\"Capture d’écran 2024-01-08 à 20.29.03\" width=\"690\" height=\"423\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Capture d’écran 2024-01-08 à 20.29.03</span><span class=\"informations\">1910×1172 109 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Be sure to use a Date column, and check theses values :</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/e/5e6a0ae86d53929f4f50f98f547b5424aeab078f.png\" title=\"Capture d’écran 2024-01-08 à 20.34.08\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/5/e/5e6a0ae86d53929f4f50f98f547b5424aeab078f_2_521x499.png\" alt=\"Capture d’écran 2024-01-08 à 20.34.08\" width=\"521\" height=\"499\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Capture d’écran 2024-01-08 à 20.34.08</span><span class=\"informations\">726×696 25.7 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Best regards,</p>"
